meta.description: Adds satisfying sounds for stepping on, hitting, breaking, and placing a wide variety of blocks that do not have their own specialized sound.
meta.long_description:
![Quality Sounds](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/ZAfRfkTo/images/a0c61e5ef90fdb52bcfc1e0c6d48a326bc370577.png)

Say goodbye to repetitive stone and wood sounds for every block. Quality Sounds gives each block its own unique, high-quality audio profile for placing, breaking, stepping, and hitting. Every sound matches the block's physical characteristics, adding realism and immersion to your block interactions.

Each wood type and leaf block gets custom sounds that fit its real life counterpart's density, texture, and flexibility. Stripping the bark off a log will remove the crunch of its bark when interacting with it. Barrels produce a hollow thunk, and wooden objects sound match the sound of their respective wood type.

Magma sizzles and ice blocks clink, while packed ice is crunchier. Because ores have distinct sounds, cave mining is easier. Glass gives off a subtle ring when placing it and glass shatter is replaced with a much improved version, to name a few.

Features

- Over 50 distinct sound groups with more planned - Individual sound groups can be enabled/disabled in the config. - Currently, the mod is available for 1.19.3 - 1.20.2 for Fabric, and 1.19.2 - 1.20.2 for Forge, with plans for additional support

Requirements

Fabric: [Fabric API](https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api/) Forge: [Cloth Config API](https://modrinth.com/mod/cloth-config)

Added Blocks

- Acacia Leaves/Sapling - Acacia Log/Wood - Acacia Button/Door/Fence/Gate/Pressure Plate/Sign/Trapdoor - Acacia Planks/Slab/Stairs/Stripped Log/Stripped Wood - Barrel - Beehive - Birch Leaves/Sapling - Birch Log/Wood/Trapdoor - Birch Button/Door/Fence/Gate/Pressure Plate/Sign - Birch Planks/Slab/Stairs/Stripped Log/Stripped Wood - Bookshelf - Chest - Bricks - Clay - Cobblestone - Copper Ore - Dark Prismarine - Deepslate Copper Ore - Deepslate Gold Ore - Deepslate Iron Ore - Emerald - End Stone - End Stone Brick - Glass/Glowstone/Beacon/Redstone Lamp/Sea Lantern - Gold Block - Gold Ore - Gravel - Hay Bale - Ice - Iron - Iron Bar/Trapdoor/Hopper/Cauldron - Iron Ore - Jungle Leaves/Sapling - Jungle Log/Wood/Button/Planks etc. - Lapis/Glazed Terracotta Blocks - Loom - Magma Block - Mangrove Leaves - Mangrove Log/Wood - Mangrove Button/Door/Fence/Gate/Pressure Plate/Sign/Trapdoor - Mangrove Planks/Slab/Stairs/Stripped Log/Stripped Wood - Mossy Cobblestone - Mossy Stone Bricks - Oak & Dark Oak Log/Wood - Respawn Anchor/Enchanting Table/Ender Chest - Andesite/Diorite/Granite - Packed/Blue Ice - Prismarine/End Stone - Quartz variants/Diamond Block/Obsidian/Crying Obsidian/Redstone Block - Raw Gold Block - Sandstone - Spruce Leaves/Sapling - Spruce Button/Door/Fence/Gate/Pressure Plate/Sign/Trapdoor - Spruce Planks/Slab/Stairs/Stripped Log/Stripped Wood - Stone Bricks - Terracotta/Bedrock Sound effects obtained from https://www.zapsplat.com under [ZapSplat Standard License](https://zapsplat-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/ZapSplat-EULA-Standard-License.pdf) for Gold Members.
